replies.body:
I play Pharah, Widow and Tracer mainly. I'm also a decent McCree, but a lot less than Pharah. I have a cousin that bought the game when it came out and he told me the general rule is to know a hero from each category, so I still need to practice Zarya for tank and Lucio for support but I pretty much suck at both xD. Though when given a decent team I can really destroy as a Pharah.

Edit: I rarely play comp because I usually have to switch to something I'm not comfortable with so for now I'm just playing qp.
